Package: ggsector
Title: Draw Sector in R
Version: 1.5.5
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Pengdong",
           family = "Yan",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           email = "yanpd01@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2425-7930"))
Description: The "ggsector" is an R package that can use "grid" or "ggplot2" to easily draw sectors. At the same time, "ggsector" provides some cases of how to call `grid.sector` in "ComplexHeatmap", and provides a function to interface with "Seurat" to facilitate the display of cell markers.
